snippet.title: Nocked! Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for Nocked! True Tales of Robin Hood. Our Steam page is now live! You can buy the game on Steam at:
 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1073840/Nocked_True_Tales_of_Robin_Hood/

Get a full bundle of great writing on itch.io: https://manofnottingham.itch.io/nocked-true-tales-of-robin-hood

And sample the gorgeous 83-minute soundtrack: https://manofnottingham.bandcamp.com/releases
